OL,7,FRail firms in South East England have
OL,8,Fannounced a ban on e-scooters due to
OL,9,Fconcerns over fire risks.
OL,11,FSoutheastern, Southern Rail,
OL,12,FThameslink and Gatwick Express will
OL,13,Fno longer allow customers aboard
OL,14,Ftheir trains with e-scooters from 1
OL,15,FJune.
OL,17,FThe decision was prompted by a series
OL,18,Fof incidents where the lithium-ion
OL,19,Fbatteries used to power e-scooters
OL,20,Fignited, raising fears about the
OL,21,Fdangers posed to passengers.
